{"tid":1562191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於2014年嘅失敗","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:23:09.000Z","uid":135593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7dbc37f9a9db33e9df95b771f84997182320f991","tid":1562191,"uid":135593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得大家仲未走到出去2014年嘅陰霾，一有少少唱歌活動，大家就好驚會輸，但其實我地可唔可以反省出，根本唔關唱歌本身事，關鍵在於我地嘅心態。<br />\n<br />\n好多人係驚大家嘅心態會趨向嘉年華而輸，但大家除左一尾靠屌佢地，有無諗過點利用依樣野去聚軍心？<br />\n<br />\n例如，大家可以完嘅時候大叫915 大遊行！之類嘅行程宣傳，令啲人keep住左唱歌個種氣勢，之後就大左機會會去。仲有好多其他香港人一定諗到點做。因為依場運動俾我睇到香港人創意超強，我覺得大家都可以用創意去走出2014之陰，令我地抗爭光譜寬左，更有可能走向2020之春。"},{"pid":"6a1aa06b5d958d3575eebddf62fb05de51839624","tid":1562191,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:21:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"54f61834867ebde20e485c8473e625c579fa030d","tid":1562191,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}